snippet.textDisplay:
Amber Heard in Aquaman.
Rumours of Amber Heard being fired from the Aquaman franchise have emerged again, but they are reportedly not true

Several reports of Amber Heard being fired from Aquaman 2 have emerged online, leading the actress to trend on social media. The reports have been debunked by The Hollywood Reporter staff writer Ryan Parker, who took to social media to state he’s been told by a “reliable source" that the reports of Heard’s alleged firing are “inaccurate."

Following the emergence of the reports on Sunday, Parker tweeted, “Told by a reliable source that reports of Amber Heard being fired off ‘Aquaman 2’ are inaccurate."

Told by a reliable source that reports of Amber Heard being fired off 'Aquaman 2' are inaccurate.— Ryan Parker (@TheRyanParker) February 28, 2021

Amber Heard Strongly Reacts to 'Paid Campaign' for Her Removal from Aquaman 2


Johnny Depp Wants Defamation Trial Against Amber Heard Postponed As It Clashes With 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Shoot

This is not the first time rumours of the actress being fired have spread, seemingly stemming from her public legal battle with ex-husband Johnny Depp. Both Depp and Heard have contested the other was physically and verbally abusive during their relationship.


Depp has already been fired from Warner Bros.’ Fantastic Beasts franchise, which also caused some to wonder why Heard wasn’t receiving the same fate, reported

Heard plays Xebellian princess Mera in the DCEU, ever since her first appearance in 2017’s Justice League. She went on to have a prominent role in 2018’s Aquaman and will reprise the part next month for Zack Snyder’s Justice League.

snippet.textDisplay:
Hey guys - #1. Where is that petition as I do want to sign I???. #2 I agree with your whole outlook on this farce of a situation. After reading and researching plus all of the legal evidence shown that she was by no means a victim. No way. She had a plan and that was from the beginning to use J.D. She is not an actress of any calibre specially when you look at what happened with Katie Holmes (now this is a woman who paid her dues and grew the talent that was already there in the first place); Warner Bros. is in hot waters because it seems their main goal is to use people and capitalize on what they can get out of them. They deserve all the hardship their actions from the past up til now has gotten them.. JD has been raked over the coals and dropped without shame (ok so they had to pay him a great amount and I believe he deserved whatever he got) and, he deserves to be granted a public apology and to be reinstated. Now we all know he made a BAD decision with his choice and has been paying dearly for it. Enough is enough. When I think of all of the other actresses past and presently who have been real victims, who have had to suffer real ndignities from the powers that be; makes me want to puke. Finally something is being done to form a movement that is now strong enough to hold people accountable and this person has the gall to do and act in a manner so demeaning of JD and of all these other women as well as the rest of us females is really Unacceptable. She will continue being a selfish, self-centered person that she is until something happens where it will devastate her so totally, that maybe, just maybe she'll learn how to really become a decent human being.
Am not wishing anything on or to her but hey what you put out always comes back. Karma's a real bitch.
